summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Thomas H. Dempsey and Rowena R. Dempsey, his wife, to the City of Seattle dated the 23rd day of February, 1909, to portions of Lots one (1), two (2), three (3), four (4), five (5), six (6), seven (7) and eight (8), Block fourteen (14) McKenzie & Dempsey's Lake Washington Addition to the City of Seattle.
